			Company Description 
		


                Banro Corp. engages in the exploration and development of gold properties. It holds interests in the Twangiza, Kamituga, Lugushwa and Namoya projects. The company was founded by Arnold T. Kondrat on May 3, 1994 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
            




